title: Alcatel switches (>=AOS7): Board Temperatures
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/alcatel
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors board temperatures on Alcatel switches running
 operating system AOS7 or higher and supporting the ALCATEL-IND1-CHASSIS-MIB
 (version for >=AOS7). Considered board temperatures are control module boards
 (CPMA and CPMB), fabric boards (CFMA, CFMB, CFMC and CMFD), fantrays 1 und 2
 (FTA und FTB) and network interface boards in slot 1 to slot 8 (NI1 to NI8).

inventory:
 One service is created for each connected board connected to the switch.

